1.  Flow of OAuth vs JWT

     [ User ]
        |
        | Click "Login with Google"
        v
    [ Frontend ]
        |
        | Redirect (OAuth Request)
        v
    [ Google OAuth ]
        |
        | Auth + Consent
        v
    [ Frontend ] <--- Authorization Code ---
        |
        | Send code
        v
    [ Backend ]
        |
        | Exchange code
        v
    [ Google OAuth ]
        |
        | access_token + id_token (JWT)
        v
    [ Backend ]
        |
        | Verify JWT, create session
        v
    [ App Authenticated ]
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.    Google OAuth flow

        [ Client ]
            |
            | OAuth Login
            v
        [ Google OAuth ]
            |
            | id_token
            v
        [ Auth Service ]
            |
            | Issue JWT + Refresh Token
            v
        [ Client ]
            |
            | API Calls with JWT
            v
        [ Microservices ]
            |
            | Validate JWT locally (no DB call)
            v
        [ Scalable System 🚀 ]

